{"tid":1871176,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺大將冇腦　拍片玩肺炎辱華","createTime":"2020-02-09T09:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T13:10:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3efbf9976e2e691d2c8482f24b2bb81bb6310edd","tid":1871176,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎肆虐全球，人人叫苦連天，但熱刺中場迪利阿里竟然將咁嚴肅嘅事情攞嚟玩，拍片影住1位操中國口音嘅華人，嘲諷對方就係新冠肺炎，涉嫌種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n事緣迪利阿里喺希斯路機場等候轉機期間，戴住黑色口罩玩自拍，仲放上社交網。從片中聽到有中國口音嘅人士說話，迪利阿里對住鏡頭講：「詳細聽下，呢個就係新冠肺炎病毒。」<br />\n<br />\n之後迪利阿里將鏡頭轉移至對方，影埋消毒洗手液，但呢位仁兄並唔知道自己已上鏡。迪利阿里又話：「病毒要嚟捉我，都係快啲走人。」迪利阿里呢段片出街之後，備受各界批評，佢受壓之下，隨即刪除片段，並作出公開道歉。<br />\n<br />\n最諷刺係迪利阿里上月尾仲喺國內微博，發貼祝賀中國鼠年快樂，支持抗疫，點知轉個頭，就拍出呢段片，可見佢極之虛偽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200209170502537-0209_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fnewe%2Findex.html%3FarticleId%3Dbkn-20200209170502537-0209_00882_001%26whichpage%3D1&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqg4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=1400f23b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200209170502537-0209_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1</a>"},{"pid":"ba47f7a095c73e86b0c74083d4ea89527c1c3621","tid":1871176,"uid":206337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"Hoball"},{"pid":"c61e9b02c51dc18548f2056d44711aad2fb8bac6","tid":1871176,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c0b44c8a23e6c94e547aef3afdbea27f4497fb","tid":1871176,"uid":168567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"c4f2cb5c3e5f3e19aa6a28a39ec1b29bd869ea4a","tid":1871176,"uid":98993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit